  "questions": [
    {
      "text": "A 34-year-old refugee presents to your family medicine clinic for an initial assessment. He has proficient English language skills, and you can communicate without an interpreter. The patient has not seen a physician since arriving in Canada two months ago. His medical history is unremarkable and vaccinations are up-to-date. Which one of the following is the most appropriate next step?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Assess thyrotropin levels."
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Screen for mental health disorders."
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Administer tetanus diphtheria acellular pertussis (Tdap) booster."
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Order an ECG."
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "text": "Send urine cultures."
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>Routine screening for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=i60JkS&anker=Za09b3ec4cbcf889fc4f7b34cecb45f4d\" data-learningcard-id=\"i60JkS\" data-anker=\"Za09b3ec4cbcf889fc4f7b34cecb45f4d\" data-section-id=\"8FcOPV0\" data-sememe-id=\"c6aaPl\">thyroid</a> dysfunction is not recommended in asymptomatic adults without <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ps0LDh&anker=Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-learningcard-id=\"ps0LDh\" data-anker=\"Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-section-id=\"FfWgLk0\" data-sememe-id=\"b31HSg0\">risk factors</a>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=AT0Rt2&anker=Zbc03040ec893396d15c13d0b69e3dba4\" data-learningcard-id=\"AT0Rt2\" data-anker=\"Zbc03040ec893396d15c13d0b69e3dba4\" data-section-id=\"XK19U30\" data-sememe-id=\"jKa_Tl\">Thyrotropin</a> levels are also not part of the routine immigration examination screening.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) CORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"wichtig\"><b>Refugees</b></span> are at <span class=\"wichtig\"><b>elevated risk for mental health conditions,</b></span> such as <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=-80D63&anker=Z2b5a77ee2051fee6724ad813948b6748\" data-learningcard-id=\"-80D63\" data-anker=\"Z2b5a77ee2051fee6724ad813948b6748\" data-section-id=\"8YdOIo0\" data-sememe-id=\"NUd-W60\">posttraumatic stress disorder</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Kv0UaR&anker=Zcd2665c9b62eca1f4af466f6d45fb223\" data-learningcard-id=\"Kv0UaR\" data-anker=\"Zcd2665c9b62eca1f4af466f6d45fb223\" data-sememe-id=\"Qj1uZS0\">depression</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=lP0vUT&anker=Zc976bd566b088e2ef27e89075ef2cbdb\" data-learningcard-id=\"lP0vUT\" data-anker=\"Zc976bd566b088e2ef27e89075ef2cbdb\" data-section-id=\"kFXmR-\" data-sememe-id=\"KlbUBF\">adjustment disorders</a>, due to trauma and resettlement stressors. Guidelines mandate that all refugees receive a comprehensive <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=HJ0KvS&anker=Z5208bc2efbfd3c982ffbeacf78ebfcb3\" data-learningcard-id=\"HJ0KvS\" data-anker=\"Z5208bc2efbfd3c982ffbeacf78ebfcb3\">medical examination</a> upon entry, which includes screening for communicable diseases, mental health screening, medical, dental, and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=cp0aoS&anker=Z8473446b734702b73ac2972b7bbf7bf7\" data-learningcard-id=\"cp0aoS\" data-anker=\"Z8473446b734702b73ac2972b7bbf7bf7\" data-section-id=\"Dvc1Xe0\" data-sememe-id=\"fm1kUh0\">vision</a> evaluations, as well as a review of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-sememe-id=\"IL0Y_g\">vaccination</a> status. This standardized, holistic approach is required to ensure early identification and management of both acute and long-term health issues and to support successful integration into the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Np0-pS&anker=Z368aa218deacf4e423a5315715333612\" data-learningcard-id=\"Np0-pS\" data-anker=\"Z368aa218deacf4e423a5315715333612\">healthcare system</a>.<br><br><span class=\"wichtig\"><b>Key learning point</b></span>: Initial refugee health assessments should include mental health, medical, dental, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=cp0aoS&anker=Z8473446b734702b73ac2972b7bbf7bf7\" data-learningcard-id=\"cp0aoS\" data-anker=\"Z8473446b734702b73ac2972b7bbf7bf7\" data-section-id=\"Dvc1Xe0\" data-sememe-id=\"fm1kUh0\">vision</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-sememe-id=\"IL0Y_g\">vaccination</a> screening to address the full spectrum of health needs.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>This patient's <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-sememe-id=\"IL0Y_g\">vaccinations</a> are up-to-date. Administering an additional booster without indication would not be appropriate or supported by <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Z2148e752962519f526f80b9aae6e8e2f\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Z2148e752962519f526f80b9aae6e8e2f\" data-section-id=\"KRcULX0\" data-sememe-id=\"M0XMg9\">immunization</a> guidelines.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>An <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pl0LBT&anker=Zf57bff8d5455c72457da0440f636f4bc\" data-learningcard-id=\"pl0LBT\" data-anker=\"Zf57bff8d5455c72457da0440f636f4bc\" data-sememe-id=\"jn0_Gg\">ECG</a> is not indicated in a healthy, asymptomatic adult with no personal or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=En08Eg&anker=Z0ccd21fcf57fab20ffb12c037f4d9af3\" data-learningcard-id=\"En08Eg\" data-anker=\"Z0ccd21fcf57fab20ffb12c037f4d9af3\" data-section-id=\"ol10BS0\">family history</a> of cardiac disease, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7S04af&anker=Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"7S04af\" data-anker=\"Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-sememe-id=\"Yk0nmT\">arrhythmia</a>, or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ps0LDh&anker=Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-learningcard-id=\"ps0LDh\" data-anker=\"Zbc0d0ff153bc5c7a27589815d0c842fd\" data-section-id=\"FfWgLk0\" data-sememe-id=\"b31HSg0\">risk factors</a>. An <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pl0LBT&anker=Zf57bff8d5455c72457da0440f636f4bc\" data-learningcard-id=\"pl0LBT\" data-anker=\"Zf57bff8d5455c72457da0440f636f4bc\" data-sememe-id=\"jn0_Gg\">ECG</a> is also not part of the routine immigration examination screening.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=kg0mv2&anker=Zb8209254add9c4f1d8b458a49671b899\" data-learningcard-id=\"kg0mv2\" data-anker=\"Zb8209254add9c4f1d8b458a49671b899\" data-section-id=\"jJX_F_\" data-sememe-id=\"R6alkl\">Urinalysis</a>, not <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7i04Gf&anker=Z0545ca944daf6c5794c76cdc4996cc3f\" data-learningcard-id=\"7i04Gf\" data-anker=\"Z0545ca944daf6c5794c76cdc4996cc3f\" data-section-id=\"YAanRM\" data-sememe-id=\"cqcaxW0\">urine culture</a>, is part of the routine immigration examination screening. Routine <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7i04Gf&anker=Z0545ca944daf6c5794c76cdc4996cc3f\" data-learningcard-id=\"7i04Gf\" data-anker=\"Z0545ca944daf6c5794c76cdc4996cc3f\" data-section-id=\"YAanRM\" data-sememe-id=\"cqcaxW0\">urine cultures</a> are not recommended in asymptomatic adults, as the yield is low and may lead to unnecessary treatment of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7i04Gf&anker=Z58d958eee4cb99180d9ff29f99319f88\" data-learningcard-id=\"7i04Gf\" data-anker=\"Z58d958eee4cb99180d9ff29f99319f88\" data-section-id=\"XAa9RM\" data-sememe-id=\"CGbqYv\">asymptomatic bacteriuria</a>.</div>",
